Unexpected = object
  case kind*: UnexpectedKind
  of Bool:
      boolValue*: bool

  of Unsigned:
      unsignedValue*: uint64

  of Signed:
      signedValue*: int64

  of Float:
      floatValue*: float64

  of Char:
      charValue*: char

  of String:
      stringValue*: string

  of Bytes:
      bytesValue*: seq[byte]

  else:
      nil
